 dabei u.a. New Weird America und Festivalkultur, Autorenfilme und »Avatar«, Indie Folk und Vollbärte sowie Neuinterpretationen von Klassikern wie Vashti Bunyan oder Ken Kesey.  afunded by Justus-Liebig-Universität Gießen  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn German.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 29. Nov 2021) 4aCultural Studies. 4aFilm. 4aKulturwissenschaft. 4aLiteratur. 4aNatur. 4aNaturinszenierung. 4aPopkultur. 4aRaumaneignung. 4aÖkologie. 7aSOCIAL SCIENCE / Popular Culture.2bisacsh  aCultural Studies.  aFilm.  aLiterature.  aNature.  aPopular Culture.1 aAnderson, Jill E., econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aAnderton, Chris, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aBonz, Jochen, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDören, Thomas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aDören, Thomas, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt1 aEbke, Thomas, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHalfacree, Keith, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aHyatt, Millay, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aKrasny, Elke, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aLander, Tobias, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aMoldenhauer, Benjamin, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aPodjed, Dan, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSicinski, Michael, econtributor.4ctb4https://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/ctb1 aSpringer, Johannes, eeditor.4edt4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/edt2 aJustus-Liebig-Universität Gießenefunder.4fnd4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/fnd08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG P